<br>
These mobs hit hard like all pop mobs but my cleric can heal my wizards a lot faster than mob can kill them, after its been slowed. <br>
<br>
Basically you have to be able to heal whoever gets summoned faster then mob can kill them. This spell is like 1500HP every 5 seconds. <br>
<br>
Supernal Remedy<br>
1: Increase Hit Points (HP) by 1450 (L61)<br>
<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Classes: Clr (L61)<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Skill: Alteration<br>
